reviewText: My toddlers just love this show
Not like the one on netflix it's kind of weird
We got this for our grandson (3 years old) and he really likes it.  He asks to see it over and over again.  As a bonus, it is very educational.
My son loves this show and was upset when it stopped airing on our local network. He learns so much from this series.

it's a really cute show but the characters can get a little annoying sometimes and my daughter seems to really like the real animals they show compared to the cartoon ones all the time but it is a great show and even teachers me some things i didn't know about even the most common animals we see everyday
